    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 13 (Spell Level 7)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 14</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 29 | <b>Successes:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 17 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 33</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You must be in a Jyuuken stance to use this technique. You make 8 Jyuuken attacks against the target, at your highest attack bonus. These attacks cannot score a critical hit and deal only half damage, but each hit deals an additional 1 point of Chakra coils damage, as well as 16 tenketsu damage. A creature's Chakra Pool cannot be reduced below 1 due to this damage. In addition, the target is stunned for 1 round, which can be saved against.<br><br>Each additional time this technique or Hyuuga Ryuu: Hakke Rokujyuuyon Shou is used against the same creature within a 24 hour period reduces the tenketsu damage per hit by 4.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
